{
  "stem": "17426.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I would say, Louise, out of the 6,000 or 7,000 that were on the [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] 90% did not make it to deck.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because on deck we were only about 500, 600, 700.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And there we saw how the ship is burning, and from time to time explosives were bursting and ripping off the deck.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't know where we are safe till we finally came to the edge of the ship and held on to one of the stanchions of the railing with our feet in between, our legs in between.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And waited.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And looked down as people were swimming, trying to swim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was all in vain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The ship was sinking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was an under draft which kept on taking them back and back and back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was still three and a half kilometers to shore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we knew-- my brother was sitting next to me-- we knew that going into the water and trying to make it would never do.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But we also knew that sitting on the ship meant certain death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At one point, somebody came-- who knew me-- with a rope, and tied it onto one of the stanchions of the railings and asked me to come with him, to lower ourself.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, what good will it do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, well, maybe we will be able to wait it out in the water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if a boat comes, or somebody comes to help us, we'll be down there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll be much closer than those that are on deck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought it made a great deal sense.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought it made sense.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
